Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.80,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.99,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Double Gauche
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.47,main,gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Double Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.12,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.51,0:23:01.69,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Spin me around like Asta did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:06.88,sign_33285_329_I_ll____kill_him,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... kill him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:06.88,main,Brother,0000,0000,0000,,Spin... Marie around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:09.88,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:14.84,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I can't disappoint Marie... \NI'll have to rely on my clone...
